FBIS4-40321 "drsov116_g_94006" FBIS-SOV-94-116 Daily Report 16 Jun 1994 WESTERN REGION Belarus Lower Russian Energy Prices `Would Help Monetary Merger' Lower Russian Energy Prices `Would Help Monetary Merger' MK1606063594 Moscow SEGODNYA in Russian 16 Jun 94 p 1 MK1606063594 Moscow SEGODNYA Russian BFN [INTERFAX report: "Minsk Asks Moscow to Revise Prices of Energy Resources"] [Text] Belorussia [Belarus] has requested the Russian Federation Government to revise the foreign trade prices of Russian energy resources. A ranking source close to the Belarussian Government has stated that "the lowering of prices of energy resources for Belorussian consumers would help a merger of the monetary systems of Russian and Belorussia."
